0:09:01,700 --> 0:09:09,440
Step 2 – Squeeze 1300g watermelon juicy from 2330g watermelon.

0:09:09,440 --> 0:09:14,920
Step 3 – Filter foam and prepare Shaban sugar.

0:09:15,000 --> 0:09:23,940
