0:09:29,920 --> 0:09:36,980
Step 6 – Add agar into watermelon juice from strainer.

0:09:37,000 --> 0:09:44,220
Step 7 – Mix and stir agar-agar and juice together gently. Divide the mixture into 12 small bowls and rest in fridge for 2 hours.

